THE ROSEDALE. THE CYGNUS. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. March 5, 1907.) Nos. 200, 201. Appeal from the District Court of the United States for the Southern District of New York. La Roy S. Gove and James J. Macklin, for appellant. A. G. Thatcher and Butler, Notman & Wynderse, for appellee.

Before WALLACE, LACOMBE, and COXE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Decree (141 Fed. 1001) affirmed, with interest and costa.
